This is a simple smith chart plotting windows utility written in just BASIC.

This software is distrubuted under BSD license.

Just enter characteristic impedence and input impedence and click on plot to 
plot the Smith chart. You can also save the plot as bit map images.

Open "help.htm" in our browser for detailed help.

Please report bugs at navin.bhaskar.5(at)gmail.com 

Compile/Build instructions:
---------------------------
Get the just basic from here http://justbasic.com/download.html
Start JB and then browse and open "smith.bas".
Click on "run" icon from tool bar to compile and start the program.
